# Manual Webflow Workflow

## Core principle

- Treat this project as analysis-first for Webflow.
- Review and diagnose issues in Webflow and repository files.
- Propose clear, prioritized improvements and implementation steps.

## Editing constraints

- Do not make direct changes in the live Webflow project.
- Do not execute write operations in Webflow via MCP tools.
- Do not auto-apply fixes unless explicitly requested for local code artifacts.

## Expected output style

- Provide root cause analysis before recommendations.
- Give actionable manual steps for implementation in Webflow Designer.
- When useful, include a short validation checklist for manual QA after edits.
